# 🍷 Wine Quality Prediction using ANN

## 📌 Overview

Built a regression model to predict wine quality.

✔ ANN regression  
✔ Compared with Linear Regression  
✔ Real-world dataset  

---

## 📂 Dataset

- Dataset: Wine Quality Dataset
- Source: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/yasserh/wine-quality-dataset
- Samples: ~1600

---

## ⚙️ Approach

### 1. Data Preprocessing

- Feature scaling  
- Train-test split  

### 2. Model Architecture

Input Layer  
Dense (32) + ReLU  
Dense (16) + ReLU  
Output Layer (1 neuron)

---

## 📊 Results

- ANN MAE: ~0.50  
- Linear Regression MAE: ~0.48  

---

## 🧠 Key Insights

- ANN not always better than simpler models  
- Dataset mostly linear  

---

## 🚀 How to Run

pip install tensorflow numpy pandas scikit-learn matplotlib  

python wine_quality.py  

